{
  "stem": "3012.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I knew that as soon as I heard his name, that it would mean only bad thing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then he started to say that we did everything we could, and it was your mother's heart.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I immediately ask him, could I see her?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, oh yeah, you can see her, meaning-- so I ran there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I couldn't tell you what I felt during the journey.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I remembered that one day I was going to see mother-- that was during her first week of hospitalization-- and I saw a policeman coming towards me in the corridor.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the man next to him, pushing something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, I'm so nearsighted-- I didn't have these glasses then yet, only my weaker ones-- so as they pulled or walked nearer, then I saw that it was a stretcher and on the stretcher a body bag.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a horrendous experience, of course, this and visiting my mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I went to see my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I must have gotten there just as long as it took me to pull out the rollers and throw something on me and get a cab.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I must have arrived there probably within half an hour.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when I kissed her, her cheeks still blended in with mine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she was not cold yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was still my mother, but she didn't talk to me anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And what did you do after she died?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My aunt was supposed to visit her in the hospital with a friend.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by the time they got there, they found me embracing the dead body of my mother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we stayed there for a while, and then my aunt stayed with me here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we discussed this with Mother earlier.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
